data.name: chkOffsetIsRelative.ToolTip
data.value: If checked, the offset is expressed as a fraction of the total length of the line to be drawn. If not checked, the offset is in pixels.

data.name: chkIntervalIsRelative.ToolTip
data.value: If checked, the interval is expressed as a fraction of the total length of the line to be drawn. If not checked, the interval is in pixels.
